data.title: A History of Irish Music
data.meta_description: A History of Irish Music - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document is an introduction from "A History of Irish Music" by William H. Grattan Flood. It provides background on the lack of a comprehensive history of Irish music and summarizes previous works. It also introduces the author's goals in writing this history, which are to consolidate sources and provide a concise yet accessible history based on 26 years of research.
